dietmate is an innovative gemini-powered app designed to personalize your diet and wellness journey.
it offers diet plans, tracks your food intake hydration, and provides real-time insights.
it is organized into five key modules:
authentication, which gathers your physical and lifestyle information to create a personalized experience;
diet planning, offering weekly diets and their customization updating them for the selected day;
calorie coach, which estimates calorie content from meal photos or text inputs and logs food and water intake;
personalized ai assistant, a cloud-based, always-available diet assistant; you can consult anything related to diet and nutrition. it listens to you while you are messaging and shapes you personal data if you accept such as updating your allergies or diseases;
reports, providing detailed tracking and analysis of your weight, calorie consumption, and hydration levels.

dietmate leverages the gemini api in multiple ways to enhance its functionality.
the gemini-powered features include creating personalized weekly diet plans, updating diets on a daily basis, estimating meal calorie content from photos or texts, and powering the intelligent chatbot that offers personalized advice, updates ypur personal preferences and answers user queries offering everything a diet mate could.
by integrating gemini apis, dietmate delivers a highly personalized and responsive experience, making it easier for users to manage their health and wellness.

